cting magnetic field exceeding $900$ G, the width of the\nsynthesized Si IV 1394 A line profile with multiple peaks can reach up to $100$\nkm s$^{-1}$, which is consistent with observations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 27 Jun 2022 06:54:20 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 27 Jul 2022 08:15:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-09-21"}
