ctable, we derive a bound for\nthe uncertainty region of the potential eavesdroppers' small-scale fading based\non a safe approximation, which facilitates the development of a block\ncoordinate descent-based iterative algorithm for obtaining an efficient\nsuboptimal solution.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 27 Jun 2022 13:49:35 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 23 Oct 2022 16:47:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-10-25"}
